    "description": "You are a lone soul who awakes in an abandoned world enveloped in flesh. As you explore, you will discover forgotten structures, abominable creatures, and fragments of your past, all twisted by the darkness now consuming the land. Your journey will be wrought with conflict, strife, and pain; you must keep going, in spite of it all. <br><br>Explore large atmospheric levels, avert enemies, cling to your resources, and solve puzzles to make your way through this world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/998c6d7ccc7ddca527f1cffcd15a02bc.poster.avif?t=1724270600\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/998c6d7ccc7ddca527f1cffcd15a02bc.webm?t=1724270600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/998c6d7ccc7ddca527f1cffcd15a02bc.mp4?t=1724270600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight your enemies when you can no longer run. Time your attacks to maximise damage output, and dodge enemy attacks to cling to your ever wavering vitality. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/e16fc499ce43b81303d3fd248a18e490.poster.avif?t=1724270600\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/e16fc499ce43b81303d3fd248a18e490.webm?t=1724270600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313220/extras/e16fc499ce43b81303d3fd248a18e490.mp4?t=1724270600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This world will wear you down the longer you persist in it; you must keep going, in spite of it all. You know there’s another way – there has to be.<br><br>-Please be aware that Never Forgotten contains several brief instances of flashing lights-",
